        <title>Hugo로 개발 블로그 장만하기</title>
        <link>https://spongebob03.github.io/p/hugo%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EC%9E%A5%EB%A7%8C%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</link>
